    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. can u get a bit more specific with the grooming stuff though? like hair and stuff. i have some clients who struggle with how to keep their hair looking \"polished\" without it looking too casual or messy for a corporate setting. what are some good examples of \"professional\" hair styles to recommend?",
