      "role": "user",
      "content": "got it. i'm thinking about some of my clients who have different hair textures though, like naturally curly or coily hair. would those styles you mentioned still work for them, or should they look into something different to make sure they don't look \"unkempt\" in a meeting? like, is there a better way for them to style it to keep that authoritative vibe?",
